A Phaser, is an energy weapon, capable of stunning or killing a living being. The Phaser has 2 main settings and levels between them. The Phaser also requires power to function and can hold up to 64K RF on itâ€™s own. It can also use any RF Energy Storage, such as a Battery. The Phaser can also be upgraded with a Weapon Modules at the Weapon Station.
To increase the level, press the right mouse button while sneaking.

    Stun

    In this setting, the phaser will do a minimal amount of damage, but it will stun the enemy for a period of time.
    
    Kill

    In this setting, the phaser will, damage and kill any living entity. The damage is proportional to the Kill setting.
